line_1: Who nature, feeling, force, expression lack;
line_2: Tragedians all, and well-arranged in black!

line_1: That the weak only and the wav'ring lack,
line_2: When they're mistaken, to conduct 'em back:
To venture forward or go back)

line_1: Next Neddy Nicely —" Fye, O fye, good lack,
line_2: "A nasty man to make his face all black."
